  m_Name: SOS Signal
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EventDefinition
  id: SOS Signal
  displayName: SOS Signal
  introText: You hear an SOS signal broadcasted from a far off asteroid in your quadrant.
    The signal is distorted so you can't quite make out exactly what they are saying
    but you can tell they are offering their skill and services in exchange for rescue.
    Its out of the way and through an astroid field but it could be worth the effort.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Rescue the stranded individual
    outcomeText: They join your crew in return, but the rescue mission took its toll.
    effects:
    - effectType: 15
      amount: 0
      secondAmount: 0
      thirdAmount: 0
      percentageOdds: 0
      crewName: 
    - effectType: 2
      amount: -10
      secondAmount: 0
      thirdAmount: 0
      percentageOdds: 0
      crewName: 
    - effectType: 1
      amount: 20
      secondAmount: 0
      thirdAmount: 0
      percentageOdds: 0
      crewName: 
  - choiceText: Ignore the signal
    outcomeText: You arrive early to trade your plundered goods and get a good price.
    effects:
